nodes.text: The Core Comestible Warehouse was a store on the planet Coruscant. It was larger in terms of size compared to Keldabe, which was a city on Mandalore. It was said that if they didn't sell the item, it didn't exist.

In 19 BBY, while waiting for the right time to extract Imperial commandos Niner and Darman Skirata in her freighter, pilot Nyreen Vollen and six Null-class Advanced Recon Commandos went to the Core Comestible Warehouse to buy supplies for Clan Skirata back on Mandalore.
